[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Written evidence from [bold]RAC Foundation[bold] (SRN 010)[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The RAC Foundation 
[normal]is a charity which explores the economic, mobility, safety and environmental issues relating to roads and responsible road users. 
[normal]Independent and authoritative research, carried out for the public benefit, is central to the Foundation’s activities.
